<paragraph id="B4585E1BF1197325FE385A1F980E3578" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Conservation status in Cameroon.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FF23BBBE0DC53BDB36AB09DA5D98D5AF" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">
<taxonomicName id="A8ABF066375FC43569CEC30A131BA17B" authorityName="Engl., Bot. Jahrb. Syst. 43 (4): 378" authorityYear="1909" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Podostemaceae" genus="Ledermanniella" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Ledermanniella linearifolia" order="Malpighiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="linearifolia">
<emphasis id="0826F486C85066A21E7D5041303261A5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Ledermanniella linearifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is listed on http://www.iucnredlist.org. It was assessed as Endangered (
<bibRefCitation id="FA471DFE06860934CFB48CE15567428B" DOI="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185505A8424796.en" author="Ghogue, J-P" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B34" refString="Ghogue, J-P, 2010f. Ledermanniellalinearifolia. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e.T185505A8424796. https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185505A8424796.en" title="Ledermanniellalinearifolia. The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species 2010: e. T 185505 A 8424796." url="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2010-3.RLTS.T185505A8424796.en" year="2010 f">Ghogue 2010f</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="2726867CC9B2B466792F151C43F19242" author="Onana, JM" journalOrPublisher="Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" refId="B66" refString="Onana, JM, Cheek, M, 2011. Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew" title="Red data list of the flowering plants of Cameroon: IUCN Global Assessments." year="2011">Onana and Cheek (2011)</bibRefCitation>
reassessed this species and maintained the Endangered status. The taxon is known from 6 localities. The extent of occurrence of 
<taxonomicName id="CD26D018C35F06931C32EBF706E620D4" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="L." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="L. linearifolia" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="linearifolia">
<emphasis id="FC7B6DB2D89CA9776B11CC132752BC12" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">L. linearifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is about 42,848,649 km2 and the area of occupancy is about 16 km2. The main threats currently known from the localities are agriculture and touristic activities. Based on these threats, the number of localities currently known, and the continuous decline of vegetation cover in the area, extent and /or quality of habitat, 
<taxonomicName id="959CCDDC9F88C59CE1379ED14BC3AF75" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="L." higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="L. linearifolia" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="81" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="species" species="linearifolia">
<emphasis id="A2CAE4ACE47A04C39423CD0FDF48C599" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">L. linearifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is currently reassessed and maintained as Endangered. IUCN Red List Category: 
<emphasis id="3AC70E83865A872F38DC2E4FC54D39E5" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="81">Endangered ENB2ab (iii).</emphasis>
</paragraph>
